=== How to build tiptop ===

* In-directory

1.  ./configure [--prefix=/some/where]
2.  For now, check the first lines of the Makefile, edit as needed.
3.  make
(4. optional)  make install



* In another directory

1.  mkdir build-dir
2.  cd build-dir
3.  /path/to/tiptop/configure  [--prefix=/some/where]
4.  For now, check the first lines of the Makefile, edit as needed.
5.  make
(6. optional)  make install